g, which is pretty intense.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.082709,0.14962,0.12589,0.11295,0.089237,0.078742,0.075344,0.066226,0.060361,0.056147,0.054,0.048777],"unified_progress":[0.094916,0.12629,0.10696,0.097733,0.089699,0.088665,0.079016,0.082704,0.070423,0.063922,0.05533,0.044338]},{"section":6,"text":"It's also limited to the right side of his head, so it's not a generalized headache like a migraine or tension headache.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.073693,0.11872,0.11259,0.10376,0.091938,0.086391,0.083801,0.078217,0.072828,0.067528,0.061363,0.049169],"unified_progress":[0.079428,0.10481,0.099002,0.097528,0.092017,0.094318,0.085596,0.08962,0.079147,0.072934,0.060716,0.044878]},{"section":7,"text":"He also mentions tearing and reddening of the right eye along with nasal stuffiness.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.067544,0.12848,0.11801,0.11202,0.09557,0.088783,0.085999,0.075824,0.066888,0.059425,0.054617,0.046835],"unified_progress":[0.081686,0.11589,0.10413,0.10154,0.093753,0.092945,0.083499,0.085274,0.07837,0.064923,0.054689,0.043295]},{"section":8,"text":"Tearing and redness in one eye could indicate some kind of irritation or inflammation.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.067988,0.094648,0.10094,0.10647,0.098131,0.094354,0.092316,0.084551,0.076806,0.071047,0.06108,0.051672],"unified_progress":[0.069058,0.09277,0.097516,0.10129,0.096882,0.096111,0.091164,0.089675,0.082461,0.073573,0.061629,0.047868]},{"section":9,"text":"Nasal stuffiness suggests possible sinus issues.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.050163,0.079346,0.093661,0.10299,0.10128,0.099856,0.098949,0.091732,0.083694,0.078181,0.06594,0.054209],"unified_progress":[0.053999,0.082682,0.093711,0.099617,0.10023,0.09824,0.095653,0.092692,0.08781,0.078786,0.066062,0.050514]},{"section":10,"text":"Maybe it's related to sinus headaches